<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١٢٧ - أبو عثمان السكوني <span class="c2">(١٥٢)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(النسائي)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(طب: ٢٨ ر / ٤ ش)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(تس: ٢٢ ر / ٣ ش)</span>، و <span class="c2">(تهـ: ٣ ر / ١ ش)</span>، و <span class="c2">(تق ٣ ر / ٢ ش)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>